    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chorizo & sweet potato quesadillas are cooking, chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomato </strong>and<strong> chopped coriander</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>reserved chopped onion</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the juice of your<strong> lime[s]</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>salsa</strong></p>",
